<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.285320>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 5. Dipoena cidae new species: (1 – 3) Male: (1) palp, ventral, (2) body, dorsal, (3) body, lateral. (4 – 5) Epigynum: (4) ventral, (5) dorsal, cleared (C, conductor; E, embolus; FS, first spermathecae; MA, median apophysis; SS, second spermathecae; T, tegulum). Scale bars: 0.25 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/285320/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

